name: Dead End (itch) (pawloKoder, omniowl, smsanderz)
description:
• You are a legion…
  • Part of an abandoned necromancer skeleton army locked away in a dungeon…
  • Reach the Necromancer’s Staff to escape the unending maze of death…
  • As many un-deaths as it takes!

Play it on a web browser (chrome, PC/Mac): https://coherence.io/games/cirocontns/ngj23-dead-end

If you don't see the server available, please reach out to us and we'll turn it on for you!

This is a Nordic Game Jam 2023 project of:

  • Ciro Continisio - Code
  • Sarah Sander - Narrative & Level Design
  • Mads Sønderstrup - Programmer, Sound & Design
  • Pawel - Some code & Slacking around
